37
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,040
Quan Rumu,

38
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:39,310
broad-minded,

39
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:41,070
died due to others' jealousy and hatred.

40
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:42,750
Long Weiyun, despite the boundary
between humans and demons,

41
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:44,600
died because of her devotion.

42
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,560
Wangquan Fugui,

43
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:48,070
only hatred

44
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:50,480
is the strongest power in the world.

45
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,950
Break the circle.

46
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:53,560
If you become one with Madam,

47
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:56,240
no one will be able to stop you!

48
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,120
Come on.

49
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,480
Rule the world together with Madam

50
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:02,430
and become the strongest ruler
in this world!

51
