101
00:11:00,710 --> 00:11:01,790
Isn't it?

102
00:11:01,810 --> 00:11:02,960
Of course not.

103
00:11:03,540 --> 00:11:05,870
When you become this world's only savior,

104
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,320
