133
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:10,780
You're quibbling!

134
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,670
You're angry?

135
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,600
You're enraged?

136
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:21,390
Then let me tell you.

137
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:23,590
Everything I said is right.

138
00:13:23,710 --> 00:13:24,750
What Black Fox?

139
00:13:24,750 --> 00:13:26,000
What Yiqi Alliance?

140
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:28,990
Inside the circle or beyond the circle,

141
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:31,200
I should be the supreme one.

142
00:13:32,270 --> 00:13:33,000
Let's

143
00:13:33,630 --> 00:13:35,270
