145
00:13:42,070 --> 00:13:43,670
Things have come to this.

146
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:48,790
All you need to do now

147
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,390
is trust me.

148
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,000
Kill!

149
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:14,960
Inside the circle or beyond the circle,

150
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:16,490
I should be the supreme one.

151
