-From love arises fear.
-From love arises fear.

162
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:46,720
Fugui.

163
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,080
It's you.

164
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:49,080
-Fugui.
-Fugui.

165
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,400
Why has your hair changed color?

166
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:53,390
I missed you so much.

167
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:55,790
Zelan Hall is disbanded today.

168
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:57,840
You've been given 3 days

169
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,630
to leave Qianji City!

170
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:02,630
Fugui.

171
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:04,240
This...

172
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:05,360
What's wrong with you?

173
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:06,390
Are you sick?

174
00:15:13,660 --> 00:15:15,080
-Fugui.
-Go, stand over there properly!

175
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:15,600
Go back!

176
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:17,000
Stand up!

177
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:17,360
Go back!

178
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:17,750
Stop!

