under Governor's order,

196
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:07,580
never to be used again.

197
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,930
I'll grant those who obey my orders

198
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:21,790
dragon power to help them cultivate.

199
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,280
Those who disobey...

200
00:16:26,720 --> 00:16:27,360
shall die.

201
00:17:34,540 --> 00:17:35,880
The Soul-Devouring Umbrella?

202
00:17:35,580 --> 00:17:38,620
[Soul-Devouring Umbrella]

203
00:17:36,550 --> 00:17:38,810
It can not only disturb the user's minds,

204
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:40,790
but also transfer others' life force

205
00:17:40,790 --> 00:17:41,830
to the user.

206
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:45,010
Young Master Fugui,

207
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:47,070
didn't I say long ago

208
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:49,570
these evil things must never be used?

209
00:17:51,070 --> 00:17:53,130
Why have they been brought out again?

210
00:17:54,550 --> 00:17:56,210
I asked Jiang Bo to bring them.

211
00:17:56,650 --> 00:17:58,200
I've disbanded Zelan Hall

212
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:00,750
and reopened Asura Hall.

213
00:18:08,350 --> 00:18:09,480
Young Master Fugui!

214
00:18:10,890 --> 00:18:11,590
Don't.

215
00:18:22,070 --> 00:18:23,160
Young Master Fugui,

216
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:24,640
if you use these evil things,

217
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:26,500
you will surely suffer backlash!

218
00:18:31,790 --> 00:18:32,880
Backlash?

219
00:18:33,450 --> 00:18:34,750
I have no taboos.

220
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,720
Why would I fear backlash?

221
00:18:45,310 --> 00:18:46,350
Young Master Fugui!

222
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:47,880
Leave Qianji City quickly!

223
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:50,800
This place's no longer your Peach Village!

224
00:19:04,830 --> 00:19:06,110
Deliver this demon core

225
00:19:06,110 --> 00:19:07,310
to Young Master.

226
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:09,310
