230
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,790
Let's survive first.

231
00:19:22,550 --> 00:19:23,720
Fortunately,

232
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:26,040
this batch of demons is evil.

233
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:26,750
Mm.

234
00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,110
Young Master,

235
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:37,240
according to your order,

236
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:40,110
I caught a group of evil demons nearby

237
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:42,070
and threw them into Asura Hall

238
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:43,730
to absorb their demon powers.

239
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:44,830
Their demon powers

240
00:19:44,830 --> 00:19:46,160
will eventually transform
into spirit pearls

241
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,240
for your use.

242
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:58,730
Having their demon powers
absorbed at Asura Hall

243
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,320
must be very painful, right?

244
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:03,910
Young Master,

245
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:05,670
it's extremely painful.

246
00:20:06,030 --> 00:20:08,550
It's just that this batch of evil demons
has quite strong demon powers.

247
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:10,920
It will take some time
to separate out their cries of agony

248
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:12,250
from the spirit pearls.

249
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:14,510
Someone will surely like

250
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:17,640
these cries of agony.

251
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:19,920
There's no need

252
00:20:21,030 --> 00:20:22,630
to separate out these cries.

253
00:20:23,620 --> 00:20:24,210
Yes.

254
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,310
Fan Yunfei,

255
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:38,960
come to Qianji City at once.

256
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:05,210
Congratulations, Madam.

257
00:21:05,270 --> 00:21:06,270
Wangquan Fugui

258
00:21:06,270 --> 00:21:08,830
has been completely influenced
by the Power of Hatred within him.

259
00:21:08,830 --> 00:21:10,920
His temperament has changed drastically.

260
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:12,420
When he breaks the circle,

261
00:21:12,750 --> 00:21:14,480
you can not only break free,

262
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:16,510
but also obtain a perfect body.

263
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:20,680
Interesting.

264
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:23,000
He took another step forward.

265
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:26,070
I'm very happy.

266
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:27,960
But

267
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,020
this is not enough.

268
00:21:29,670 --> 00:21:31,680
I'll give him another push

269
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:35,030
to completely make him
the incarnation of the Power of Hatred.

270
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:36,400
Go tell Jiuwei

271
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:38,400
to find that person.

272
00:21:39,350 --> 00:21:40,550
Make good use of him.

273
00:21:40,550 --> 00:21:41,350
Yes.

274
00:21:44,980 --> 00:21:52,530
