277
00:22:58,070 --> 00:22:58,920
I'm fine.

278
00:23:01,830 --> 00:23:03,640
I inhaled some Dragon Qi

279
00:23:04,510 --> 00:23:06,400
when I killed Quan Jingting.

280
00:23:10,070 --> 00:23:11,070
That's good then.

281
00:23:12,550 --> 00:23:13,350
Master.

282
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,590
Your umbrella

283
00:23:15,790 --> 00:23:17,350
looks like an evil object.

284
00:23:23,510 --> 00:23:24,790
