285
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:28,280
It must be that I lack knowledge.

286
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,070
Master,

287
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:31,750
I already know

288
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:33,610
about what happened

289
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:37,110
to Chief Hongye and Celestial Master.

290
00:23:37,110 --> 00:23:38,440
Master, don't be sad.

291
00:23:39,680 --> 00:23:41,000
You still have me.

292
00:23:41,790 --> 00:23:42,680
I'm

293
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:45,620
willing to fight
against the Black Fox with you.

294
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:47,160
Poor Dog.

295
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:50,000
Are you...

296
00:23:51,030 --> 00:23:52,480
indebted to me?

297
00:23:53,830 --> 00:23:54,400
Mm.

298
00:23:55,830 --> 00:23:56,960
Then today,

299
00:23:58,240 --> 00:24:00,900
I want to take something
as your repayment to me.

300
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:02,480
Are you willing?

301
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:04,400
Of course.

302
00:24:09,310 --> 00:24:10,110
Master.

303
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:12,540
What are you doing?

304
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:40,440
Master.

305
00:24:41,510 --> 00:24:42,510
Why?

306
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:46,880
Why?

307
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:49,400
Because I've finally understood

308
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:50,750
good...

309
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:53,880
can't triumph over evil.

310
00:24:56,830 --> 00:24:58,230
Because neither you nor I

311
00:24:59,950 --> 00:25:01,960
can be as ruthless

312
00:25:03,030 --> 00:25:04,640
as the Black Fox,

313
00:25:06,750 --> 00:25:08,750
destroying gods and Buddhas alike.

314
00:25:16,040 --> 00:25:17,160
I don't believe

315
00:25:17,910 --> 00:25:19,170
a single word you said.

316
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:22,830
You can take the Water-Control Orb,

317
00:25:23,350 --> 00:25:25,240
but you must tell me the truth!

318
00:25:34,680 --> 00:25:35,550
Master.

319
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:38,960
Master!

320
00:25:43,310 --> 00:25:44,350
Master.

321
00:25:51,070 --> 00:25:52,030
Fan Yunfei.

322
00:25:54,830 --> 00:25:55,920
Why are you here?

323
00:25:57,030 --> 00:25:58,110
Miss Qingtong.

324
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,260
Young Master Fugui...

325
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:11,970
took your Water-Control Orb?

326
00:26:19,310 --> 00:26:20,310
Miss Qingtong,

327
00:26:21,750 --> 00:26:24,030
why has Master become like this?

328
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:27,510
You must know the reason.

329
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:29,270
Tell me, okay?

330
00:26:34,030 --> 00:26:35,090
There's no reason.

331
00:26:37,070 --> 00:26:38,590
It's exactly what you saw.

332
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:41,350
Yunfei,

333
00:26:42,070 --> 00:26:43,310
don't dwell on why Young Master Fugui

334
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:44,510
has become like this.

335
00:26:45,590 --> 00:26:46,750
If you want to live,

336
00:26:47,110 --> 00:26:48,570
leave this place quickly.

337
00:26:51,110 --> 00:26:52,160
I won't leave.

338
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:53,830
If Master wants to take everything back

339
00:26:53,830 --> 00:26:55,430
and take the Black Fox's Way,

340
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:57,750
just take my life as well.

341
00:26:58,240 --> 00:26:59,920
Otherwise, I would rather die than leave!

342
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:00,800
Fan Yunfei!

343
00:27:01,880 --> 00:27:02,680
I told you!

344
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:04,300
If you want to live,

345
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:05,440
leave now!

346
00:27:12,790 --> 00:27:14,860
You overconfident fool.

347
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:16,440
Both of you, get lost!

348
00:27:35,620 --> 00:27:36,950
The Dust-Seeker Sword?

349
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:42,220
[Dust-Seeker]

350
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,900
Why are you still here?

351
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:58,140
You don't want to leave your Qianji City?

352
00:28:02,070 --> 00:28:02,790
I...

353
00:28:09,110 --> 00:28:10,590
don't want to leave you.

354
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:15,160
I think

355
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:18,110
you shouldn't stay here waiting for death.

356
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:19,590
You people are too weak.

357
00:28:20,070 --> 00:28:20,790
To me,

358
00:28:20,790 --> 00:28:22,720
all of you are nothing but burdens.

359
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:24,680
Just get lost.

360
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:25,960
After all,

361
00:28:26,110 --> 00:28:28,270
pets shouldn't disobey their owners.

362
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:48,050
♪ It was you who opened the world,
the times transparent ♪

363
00:28:51,110 --> 00:28:53,110
Young Master Fugui
gave me the name of Qingtong

364
00:28:51,370 --> 00:28:54,850
♪ At sunrise, I open my eyes;
at moonfall, I wait for an answer ♪

365
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,540
and taught me swordsmanship,

366
00:28:56,350 --> 00:28:58,510
not to make me anyone's pet.

367
00:28:58,440 --> 00:29:01,000
♪ If the light shines through the night ♪

368
00:28:59,440 --> 00:29:00,270
You...

369
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,330
♪ Dawn will awaken ♪

370
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:05,350
are no longer that Young Master Fugui.

371
00:29:05,300 --> 00:29:08,740
♪ We never ask if fate is fair ♪

372
00:29:12,230 --> 00:29:15,910
♪ You are the bright morning,
sinking into the sea ♪

373
00:29:18,990 --> 00:29:22,380
♪ I am the reflection
of the clear puzzle in the wind ♪

374
00:29:26,020 --> 00:29:30,490
♪ If our so-called destiny
is to separate ♪

375
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:29,830
Young Master Yunfei,

376
00:29:29,830 --> 00:29:30,640
you're back.

377
00:29:32,350 --> 00:29:33,850
Leave me alone.

378
00:29:33,010 --> 00:29:36,750
♪ We'll exchange courage
in the sea and wind ♪

379
00:29:38,770 --> 00:29:43,530
♪ Through the dream, I'll meet you again ♪

380
00:29:45,620 --> 00:29:50,320
♪ Not yet awake, but I believe I'm close ♪

381
00:29:47,200 --> 00:29:48,350
Master.

382
00:29:49,510 --> 00:29:50,510
Why?

383
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:53,960
Why have you become like this?

384
00:29:52,500 --> 00:29:57,360
♪ If we're destined to not be together ♪

385
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:04,270
♪ Be each other's star
and meet at the end of destiny ♪

386
00:30:02,310 --> 00:30:03,510
What happened?

387
00:30:05,750 --> 00:30:08,080
Tell me, why would a perfectly fine person

388
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:14,880
suddenly change?

389
00:30:16,750 --> 00:30:18,750
Are you talking about Royal Master?

390
00:30:19,510 --> 00:30:20,880
I don't know why...

391
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:25,260
♪ You're ripples in the wind,
blowing away the riddles of yesterday ♪

392
00:30:22,790 --> 00:30:25,000
Master took my Water-Control Orb.

393
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:31,870
♪ Beneath the waves, I'm dawn's glow,
refracted into silken flows ♪

394
00:30:29,350 --> 00:30:31,410
I don't know what he has been through,

395
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:35,080
but he is no longer the Master
he used to be.

396
00:30:35,820 --> 00:30:40,110
♪ If our so-called destiny
is to separate ♪

397
00:30:42,350 --> 00:30:42,920
Zhao.

398
00:30:42,820 --> 00:30:46,340
♪ Amidst the sea and wind,
we wait for an echo ♪

399
00:30:44,350 --> 00:30:45,950
General, what's the matter?

400
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:48,480
Send a message
to Junior Tingyun immediately.

401
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:49,860
Tell her the Soldier's heart has changed.

402
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:53,070
♪ Through the dream, I'll meet you again ♪

403
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:53,500
And tell her to make preparations early.

404
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:54,480
Yes.

405
00:30:55,370 --> 00:31:00,250
♪ Not yet awake, but I believe I'm close ♪

406
00:31:02,180 --> 00:31:07,090
♪ If we're destined to not be together ♪

407
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:14,010
♪ I'll meet you in the sky next time
to fly far away together ♪

408
00:31:42,480 --> 00:31:43,350
Senior Fugui,

409
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:45,960
in the end, you still

410
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:47,200
took a different path.

